	(struct fmodule):
	moved from module_interface.c/h to module_list.c/h

	* fvwm/module_list.h (do_execute_module):
	* fvwm/module_interface.h (AddToCommandQueue):
	(ExecuteModuleCommand):
	initialy static functions are exposed for now. Should be fixed soon.

