	* fvwm/module_list.c (do_execute_module):
	made absolutely sure the module's read fd is >=0 before inserting
	the module on the list

	* fvwm/events.c (My_XNextEvent):
	* fvwm/module_list.c (PositiveWrite):
	(CMD_ModuleSynchronous):
	assume module read fd is allways >=0 (remove the tests)

	* fvwm/module_list.c (module_free):
	no need to test if fd >=0 when closing the pipes.

