2003-07-04  Dominik Vogt  <dominik(dot)vogt(at)gmx(dot)de>

	* libs/Bindings.c (key_modifiers):
	moved to new file wcontext.c

	* libs/gravity.c (gravity_parse_dir_argument):
	added aliases for compass directions:
	  - = N
	  _ = S
	  [ = W
	  ] = E
	  ^ = NE
	  > = SE
	  v = SW
	  [ = nw
	  . = center

