	(MoveFocus):
	(SetFocusWindow):
	(ReturnFocusWindow):
	(DeleteFocus):
	(ForceDeleteFocus):
	(FocusOn):
	(restore_focus_after_unmap):
	Fixed a race condition with M_FOCUS_CHANGE events and window updates by
	suppressing the M_FOCUS_CHANGE message if the focus does not change in
	the flush_window_updates() function.

