2001-07-29  Dominik Vogt  <dominik(dot)vogt(at)gmx(dot)de>

	* libs/XineramaSupport.c (XineramaSupportConfigureModule):
	* fvwm/modconf.c (send_xinerama_state):
	* fvwm/module_interface.c (broadcast_xinerama_state):
