2007-03-11  Scott Smedley  <ss(at)aao(dot)gov(dot)au>

	* configure.ac:
	bugfix: 'make dist' failed cos I moved 'scott.notes' to util/ subdir.
	bugfix: out-of-tree builds failed due to broken dependency.
	Make man page have same header as old one.
	Fix man page indentation.
	Make text of top-level man page sections all uppercase.
	Added --disable-mandoc option.
	HTML doc generation is off by default: use --enable-htmldoc.
	Added more info in doc/README about XML commands to use.

2007-03-10  Scott Smedley  <ss(at)aao(dot)gov(dot)au>

	* NEWS:
	* Everything in the 'doc' subdirectory.

	XML source to generate man page & HTML documentation.

