	* configure.in:
	increased version to 2.5.13
	released 2.5.12

	* ANNOUNCE:
	* NEWS:
	* configure.in:
	updated for 2.5.12 release

	* fvwm/frame.c (frame_create_move_resize_args):
	fixed xemacs growing or shrinking when title height changed; this was
	caused by calculating the old client window geometry using the new
	title dimensions; query the window size instead

