	* fvwm/conditional.c (CMD_CondCase):
	fixed CondCase command
	(CMD_Cond):
	fixed numeric return codes

	* fvwm/add_window.c (CMD_Recapture):
	fixed focus loss w/ SloppyFocus and MouseFocus after RecaptureWindow

