	return the geometry of the whole icon
	fixed $[w.height] when the window is shaded
	cleaned up icon geometry code

2002-01-17  Dominik Vogt  <dominik(dot)vogt(at)gmx(dot)de>

	* fvwm/commands.h:
	* fvwm/functions.c:
	* fvwm/functions.h:
