	* fvwm/menus.c (get_menu_options):
	(get_popup_options):
	(MenuInteraction):
	(pop_menu_up):
	handle Xinerama screens for positioning menus w/ posthints

	* fvwm/menus.c (get_menu_options):
	renamed function
	fix for icon/window context rectangle when window is in wrong state

