2001-07-06  Mikhael Goikhman  <migo@homemail.com>

	* acinclude.m4:
	Replaced forgotten instances of IMLIB_CFLAGS and IMLIB_LIBS to
	GDK_IMLIB_*.  This fixes "make FvwmGtk" on systems with bogus
	imlib-config.

